flowchart TD

    A[Legal Entity to process]

    A --> B{VAT provided by RMPM?}

    B -->|Yes| C[STATUS = PROVIDED_BY_RMPM]

    B -->|No| D{VAT computable?}

    D -->|Yes| E[Compute VAT]
    E --> F[Call VIES]

    F -->|OK| G[Update TAX_CODE<br/>STATUS = CONFIRMED_BY_VIES]

    F -->|NOT_FOUND| I

    F -->|VIES_ERROR| X[Stop processing<br/>Keep current TAX_CODE and STATUS<br/>Store VIES_ERROR<br/>Notify CRDS]

    D -->|No| I{Orbis match available?}

    I -->|Yes| K[STATUS = CONFIRMED_BY_ORBIS]

    I -->|No| L{Refinitiv match available?}

    L -->|Yes| N[STATUS = CONFIRMED_BY_REFINITIV]

    L -->|No| O[STATUS = NOT_ELIGIBLE]
